        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25638353/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25638353/" class="">第4页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/gckf/" class=" " title="陆浅浅">陆浅浅</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25638353">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">阅读使人充实，会谈使人敏捷，写作与笔记使人精确。读史使人明智，诗歌使人巧慧，数学使人精细，博物使人人深沉，伦理之学使人庄重，与修辞使人善变。------培根</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-07 21:50</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                阅读使人充实，会谈使人敏捷，写作与笔记使人精确。读史使人明智，诗歌使人巧慧，数学使人精细，博物使人人深沉，伦理之学使人庄重，与修辞使人善变。------培根
